        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yimihai/" class="name">沙漠里的一条腿</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2012-03-02" class="main-meta">2012-03-02 20:08:04</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1090042/">花城出版社1997版</a>
