            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5328150/">《流言》中的张爱玲</a></h2>

                <div id="review_5328150_short" class="review-short" data-rid="5328150">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        高中时读张爱玲的小说，尽管内心觉得是好，但不太愿意放声说出来。因为在她华美的文字下面，隐隐地透出一股幽冷怪戾之气，令还未经历人生风浪的我颇感不适。觉得读多了人也会变得凄恻起来。然而后来总算长大了，知道了人类本性的伟大：再怎样营造出的真切的情境，如果与自身生...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5328150-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_5328150_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_5328150_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="5328150" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-5328150">
                                112
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="5328150" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-5328150">
                                3
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5328150/#comments" class="reply ">4回应</a>

                    <a href="javascript:;;" class="fold hidden">收起</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

            
    
    <div data-cid="1177104">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1177104">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/riverknows/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1105282-22.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/riverknows/" class="name">riverknows</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2007-07-07" class="main-meta">2007-07-07 21:39:39</span>


